	   <tr><td colspan=2>i think you are eaither looking for spooke the dead or sense undead, these lists below are the spells you need at 9 and 15. all of them at lvl 9 are usefull. the level 15 spells are all usefull except for hammer of wrath. it costs about 5 plat and is only usefull for a corpse run. you may want to hold off on that spell till a later time. <br><br>LEVEL 9 SPELLS <br>Courage - HP(20) and AC(3) buff<br>Cure Poison - Cures target of poison effects Flash of Light - Blinds target<br>Minor Heal - Healing spell (10hp)<br>Spook the Dead - Undead only fear <br>True North - Face to the north. <br>Yaulp - Self only combat buff (str 10) (ac 6) <br><br>LEVEL 15 SPELLS <br>Cure Disease - Cures the target of disease <br>Hammer of Wrath - Summons a magical hammer&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Holy Armor - AC(6) buff <br>Light Healing - Healing spell (35hp)<br>Lull - Reduce the target's aggression  <br>Sense the Dead - Detects undead creatures <br>Ward Undead - Undead DD line of spells (41hp)<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Celtpirate Waverider<br>34 paladin<br>saryrn-Boche Morte<br>Yoshiro<br>15 cleric<br>saryrn-House of Wargoth</td></tr>
